statements: SELECT * FROM viewer_engagement_and_feedback;
SELECT event_name, event_date, engagement_rating FROM viewer_engagement_and_feedback;
SELECT viewer_name, viewer_location FROM viewer_engagement_and_feedback WHERE engagement_rating > 3;
SELECT * FROM viewer_engagement_and_feedback WHERE event_date = '2022-04-15';
SELECT event_name, engagement_rating FROM viewer_engagement_and_feedback ORDER BY engagement_rating DESC;
SELECT * FROM viewer_engagement_and_feedback WHERE engagement_rating > 4 ORDER BY event_date DESC, viewer_name ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT viewer_name, viewer_location, engagement_rating FROM viewer_engagement_and_feedback WHERE viewer_location LIKE 'New%' AND engagement_rating IN (4, 5) ORDER BY viewer_name ASC;
SELECT viewer_name, event_name, event_date FROM viewer_engagement_and_feedback WHERE viewer_id='123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000' AND engagement_rating < 3 ORDER BY event_date DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT viewer_name, engagement_rating FROM viewer_engagement_and_feedback WHERE feedback_text ILIKE '%great%' OR feedback_text ILIKE '%excellent%' ORDER BY viewer_name ASC, event_date DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT event_name, COUNT(*) AS total_feedback_count FROM viewer_engagement_and_feedback GROUP BY event_name HAVING COUNT(*) > 5 ORDER BY total_feedback_count DESC;
SELECT * FROM viewer_engagement;
SELECT viewer_id, event_id, timestamp FROM viewer_engagement WHERE viewer_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM viewer_feedback WHERE feedback_rating > 3;
SELECT viewer_id, event_id, feedback_rating FROM viewer_feedback WHERE viewer_id = 2;
SELECT viewer_id, event_id, feedback_rating, feedback_comment FROM viewer_feedback ORDER BY event_id DESC;
SELECT viewer_id, event_id, timestamp, interaction_type, interaction_details FROM viewer_engagement WHERE viewer_id = 12345 ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT * FROM viewer_engagement WHERE event_id = 56789 AND interaction_type = 'like' ORDER BY timestamp ASC;
SELECT AVG(feedback_rating) AS average_rating, event_id FROM viewer_feedback GROUP BY event_id HAVING COUNT(feedback_id) > 5;
SELECT viewer_id, event_id, feedback_rating FROM viewer_feedback WHERE event_id IN (12345, 67890, 98765) ORDER BY feedback_rating DESC;
SELECT viewer_id, event_id, feedback_rating, feedback_comment FROM viewer_feedback WHERE feedback_rating >= 4 AND feedback_comment LIKE '%Great%' ORDER BY event_id ASC;
SELECT viewer_id, event_id, engagement_level FROM viewer_engagement ORDER BY viewer_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM sports_events WHERE event_date >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY event_name DESC;
SELECT viewer_id, event_id, engagement_level FROM viewer_engagement WHERE engagement_level = 'high';
SELECT event_id, event_name, event_location FROM sports_events WHERE event_location LIKE '%stadium%';
SELECT viewer_id, event_id, feedback_text, rating FROM viewer_feedback ORDER BY rating DESC, viewer_id ASC;
SELECT viewer_id, event_id, engagement_level, feedback FROM viewer_engagement WHERE viewer_id = 100 ORDER BY event_id DESC;
SELECT event_name, event_date, event_location FROM sports_events WHERE event_date > '2022-01-01' AND event_location LIKE '%Stadium%' ORDER BY event_date ASC;
SELECT feedback_id, viewer_id, event_id, feedback_text, rating FROM viewer_feedback WHERE rating >= 4 ORDER BY viewer_id, event_id;
SELECT viewer_id, COUNT(event_id) AS total_events_engaged FROM viewer_engagement GROUP BY viewer_id HAVING total_events_engaged > 5 ORDER BY total_events_engaged DESC;

SELECT v.viewer_id, v.event_id, v.engagement_level, f.feedback_text FROM viewer_engagement v JOIN viewer_feedback f ON v.viewer_id = f.viewer_id AND v.event_id = f.event_id WHERE v.engagement_level = 'High' AND f.rating > 3 ORDER BY f.rating DESC, v.viewer_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM viewer_engagement;
SELECT event_id, viewer_id, engagement_level FROM viewer_engagement ORDER BY engagement_level ASC;
SELECT viewer_name, viewer_location FROM viewer_profiles WHERE viewer_age > 30;
SELECT viewer_id, COUNT(*) AS total_engagements FROM viewer_engagement GROUP BY viewer_id;
SELECT event_name, event_date, COUNT(*) AS total_ratings FROM event_details JOIN feedback_ratings ON event_details.event_id = feedback_ratings.event_id GROUP BY event_name, event_date;
SELECT * FROM viewer_engagement ORDER BY event_id DESC, engagement_level ASC;
SELECT event_id, viewer_id, engagement_level FROM viewer_engagement WHERE viewer_id = 1001;
SELECT event_name, event_date FROM event_details WHERE event_location = 'New York' ORDER BY event_date DESC;
SELECT viewer_name, viewer_age, viewer_location FROM viewer_profiles WHERE viewer_age > 30 ORDER BY viewer_age ASC;
SELECT event_name, viewer_name, rating FROM event_details JOIN feedback_ratings ON event_details.event_id = feedback_ratings.event_id ORDER BY rating DESC;
SELECT * FROM viewers;
SELECT viewer_name, engagement_level FROM viewers ORDER BY engagement_level DESC;
SELECT event_name, event_date, event_location FROM events WHERE event_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT viewer_name, event_name, feedback_score FROM viewers INNER JOIN feedback ON viewers.viewer_id = feedback.viewer_id;
SELECT viewer_id, event_id FROM viewers_events WHERE viewer_id = 1 AND event_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM viewers WHERE engagement_level > 3;
SELECT viewer_name, event_name FROM viewers JOIN viewers_events ON viewers.viewer_id = viewers_events.viewer_id JOIN events ON viewers_events.event_id = events.event_id;
SELECT event_name, event_location FROM events WHERE event_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT viewer_name, feedback_score, feedback_comment FROM feedback JOIN viewers ON feedback.viewer_id = viewers.viewer_id;

SELECT viewer_name, event_name, feedback_score FROM viewers JOIN viewers_events ON viewers.viewer_id = viewers_events.viewer_id JOIN feedback ON viewers.viewer_id = feedback.viewer_id AND viewers_events.event_id = feedback.event_id;
